title: Shiny Bumpers And Lights Of Vintage Cars Photo
caption: The bumpers and lights of colorful shiny cars fill the frame in a parking lot.

title: Shipping Containers In Yard Photo
caption: The colorful shipping containers stacked high in this yard, look as much like toy building blocks as giant metal box, from this height

title: The Front Headlight Of A Dark Green Car Photo
caption: The front headlight of a dark green car. The lights are orange and white.

title: Car 99 Takes the Lead In A Blur Of Speed Photo
caption: The crowd rushes by in a blur as car number 99 pulls to the lead of the race.

title: Large Teddy Bear Stuck In A Cars Open Window Photo
caption: The back half of a shiny light blue car with a large blue teddy bear caught in the open window. There is a white bus behind the blue car.

title: Plane Casts A Shadow On The Ground Photo
caption: An old plane sat on grass casts deep shadows on the ground below as the sun moves around it.

title: Streetcar Driver At Work Photo
caption: The view over the shoulder of a bus driver in his orange cubicle, autumn leaves visible through the windscreen and the lines of tram tracks.

title: Antique Trucks And Cars On Display Photo
caption: Antique trucks and cars are restored and on display for all to enjoy.

title: A Photographer Poses Overlooking The Plains With Arms Open Photo
caption: A man in shorts and a vest holds his arms up, a camera in one hand, to proclaim himself king of the world to the sprawling semi-arid plains and mountains below him.

title: Two Feet Stick Out The Front Window Of A White Car Photo
caption: Two feet with boots on them stick out the front window of a white car with a blue wood top. The car is parked with a light blue building behind it.

title: An Off Road Vehicle With Storage Strapped Down Photo
caption: The back of a red and silver off road vehicle with a tire and a black storage box strapped down.

title: Aerobatic Plane In Flight Leaving Behind A White Trail Photo
caption: A blue airplane with orange stripes and silver stars on it flies through the sky leaving behind a white trail. You can see green land below it.

title: White Trucks Lined Up In A Row Photo
caption: Several white moving trucks line up along the streets of a concrete building. A trees shadow cuts through the middle of the frame, bringing a hint of darkness.

title: A Photographer In A Desert Graveyard Of Cars Snaps A Photo Photo
caption: A man in pink shorts, a vest and a hat snaps a photo of us through a doorway. Behind a graveyard of cars and trucks gives way to the mounds of a desert.

title: Car Drives Down Cobblestone Road At Night Photo
caption: Low view of a car driving down a cobblestone road on a dark night.

title: Front Of A Bright Blue Classic Car With Round Hood Photo
caption: The front of a bright blue car with a round hood. You can see a red car in the reflection of the cars hubcap.

title: Blue And Yellow Aerobatic Plane In Flight Photo
caption: Photo of a blue and yellow single person airplane flying high above green country fields.

title: Two Lines Of Parked Bicycles Photo
caption: Two packed lines of parked bikes on a paved parking lot of bikes.

title: Shiny Black Car Truck Photo
caption: A black car gleams, not a speck of dust or dirt on either the truck or the lights, which are currently turned on.

title: Empty Black Seats On A Commercial Airplane Photo
caption: Black empty seats on an airplane illuminated by the small round windows.

title: View Down The White Line Of An Empty Paved Road Photo
caption: View down a white spotted line of an empty paved road surrounded by rust colored land. There is a single white vehicle driving on the right side of the road.

title: Night Driver Photo
caption: As a man drives through town in the night, distorted lights are seen outside of the car windshield.

title: A White Convertible Jeep With A Red And Blue Stripe Photo
caption: A white convertible Jeep with a red and blue stripe down the side of it, that is parked next to a pile of wood and a green cedar.

title: Silhouette Of A Person Sitting By An Airplane Window Photo
caption: Silhouette of a person tilting their head down with an airplane window behind them.
